---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Stay for Cultural Preservation — Protect Living Heritage">
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <p class="text-ember text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">For Culture Keepers</p>
        <h1 class="heading-lg mb-6">
          Every elder is a<br/>
          <span class="text-ember">library waiting to be preserved.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Indigenous traditions. Oral histories. Artisan techniques. Languages spoken by only a few. The knowledge that exists in people, not books — and disappears when they're gone.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Problem -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="heading-md mb-4">The urgency of cultural preservation</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center mb-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">1 language</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Dies every 2 weeks, taking unique knowledge with it</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">90%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Of world's languages may be lost by 2100</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-4xl font-serif text-ember mb-2">Countless</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-parchment-muted">Traditions exist only in memory of elders</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          When an elder passes, we don't just lose a person — we lose a connection to centuries of accumulated wisdom, stories, and ways of understanding the world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use Cases -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-12">Preserving living heritage</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Indigenous Elders</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Creation stories. Traditional practices. Ecological knowledge. Spiritual teachings. All preserved in the elder's own voice, in their own language.
            </p>
            <p class="text-ember text-sm font-medium">
              100% on-device processing means sensitive cultural knowledge stays private.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Language Preservation</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Record fluent speakers telling stories, explaining words, singing songs. Capture pronunciation, idioms, and context that dictionaries can't preserve.
            </p>
            <p class="text-ember text-sm font-medium">
              Transcription supports multiple languages with the voice preserved.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.232 5.232l3.536 3.536m-2.036-5.036a2.5 2.5 0 113.536 3.536L6.5 21.036H3v-3.572L16.732 3.732z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Artisan Knowledge</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              Master craftspeople explaining techniques: blacksmiths, weavers, potters, woodworkers. The subtle knowledge that takes decades to acquire, explained step by step.
            </p>
            <p class="text-ember text-sm font-medium">
              Document processes in the artisan's own voice and terminology.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-void-50 p-8 border border-void-200">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif mb-4">Veterans & Witnesses</h3>
            <p class="body-md text-parchment-muted mb-4">
              First-hand accounts of historical events. Veterans' stories. Witnesses to moments that shaped history. Preserved before living memory becomes only written history.
            </p>
            <p class="text-ember text-sm font-medium">
              Personal accounts in the speaker's own voice and perspective.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Quote -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <blockquote class="text-center">
          <p class="font-serif text-2xl text-parchment mb-6 italic">
            "When an old man dies, a library burns to the ground."
          </p>
          <cite class="text-parchment-muted">— African proverb</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- For Organizations -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <h2 class="heading-md text-center mb-8">For cultural organizations</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-center text-parchment-muted mb-12">
          Museums, cultural centers, tribal organizations, and heritage groups can use Stey to empower community members to capture their own stories.
        </p>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">No specialized equipment</h4>
              <p class="body-sm text-parchment-muted">Just an iPhone — elders can record independently</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">Automatic transcription</h4>
              <p class="body-sm text-parchment-muted">On-device AI transcribes in multiple languages</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">Data sovereignty</h4>
              <p class="body-sm text-parchment-muted">All data stays on device — full community control</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-ember/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ember" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-serif text-lg mb-1">Exportable archives</h4>
              <p class="body-sm text-parchment-muted">Export to standard formats for institutional archives</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-void-50">
      <div class="container-narrow text-center">
        <h2 class="heading-md mb-6">Preserve what books cannot.</h2>
        <p class="body-lg text-parchment-muted mb-8">
          Start capturing living heritage today.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-parchment text-void px-8 py-4 font-medium hover:bg-ember transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/>
          </svg>
          Download for iOS — Free
        </a>
        <p class="text-parchment-dark text-sm mt-4">
          Cultural organization? <a href="/contact" class="text-ember hover:underline">Contact us</a> about institutional programs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
